      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Reduce latency by tuning configuration parameters. For Chatterbox, adjust batch sizes and concurrency limits based on load testing. Implement caching for frequent queries and use connection pooling to minimize overhead. Profile model inference to identify slow operations and consider hardware acceleration if applicable."
          }
