            "type": "text",
            "text": "Establish alerts for latency thresholds to proactively address issues. Regularly review performance trends and update configurations as traffic patterns change. Automate scaling to handle load spikes without degrading latency, and conduct periodic audits of dependencies to ensure optimal integration."
